{"id": 2659, "genre": 1001, "title": "你发现当代人有哪些生活环节都被搬进了商场里？", "description": "逛公园变成逛宜家，小卖部买买买变成进口超市买买买。（题图来自：iStock ©️ beastfromeast）", "record_count": 1959, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181204112539vMjPxac5H6zSlqiV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 316164, "content": "不想去商场的时候也想不出能去哪里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881225}, {"id": 315658, "content": "读报看书写作业，星巴克肯德基必胜客", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 315659, "content": "Cool\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525937}, {"id": 315661, "content": "吃完饭去KTV", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145815}, {"id": 315663, "content": "小朋友的童年", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58899}, {"id": 315665, "content": "按摩 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506780}, {"id": 317457, "content": "夏日商场避暑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495478}, {"id": 315668, "content": "去宜家吃饭逛街", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433706}, {"id": 315670, "content": "和家人在一起的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428010}, {"id": 315671, "content": "hh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528006}, {"id": 315673, "content": "逛街变成逛商场", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057898}, {"id": 315675, "content": "带娃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527977}, {"id": 315676, "content": "带娃", "image": "img/option/option/20181210120406RKXixcO4YVrWC5FT", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527977}, {"id": 315678, "content": "站在扶梯边上刷大众点评，纠结吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894776}, {"id": 316190, "content": "谈恋爱逛商场", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530097}, {"id": 315680, "content": "和老朋友聚会，都是先去商场去看个电影在吃个饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528022}, {"id": 315684, "content": "咖啡“外卖”自取：商场里的take-out咖啡店，在门口拿手机下单，进店自取。#附：黑人问号脸#", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467698}, {"id": 315689, "content": "商场里一定要有可以拍照的地方，不然不去哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528044}, {"id": 315692, "content": "一有内急首先想到的还是找个附近的商场", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420650}, {"id": 315697, "content": "要写点儿东西还真的必须去咖啡店，伴随着略微嘈杂的白噪音，家里太安静反而不行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 315700, "content": "取暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526111}, {"id": 315701, "content": "好像聚会什么的基本都是先吃饭后ktv", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396323}, {"id": 315702, "content": "这一年我发现已经没有街道，印象中的“街”已被“商场”取代。", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400307}, {"id": 315703, "content": "冬天去商场蹭暖气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 315704, "content": "童年的欢笑声，生活的烟火气~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528135}, {"id": 315705, "content": "免费的空调 免费的休息  免费的充电宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949293}, {"id": 315706, "content": "免费蹭WiFi的地方，夏天去商城享受免费空调。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528165}, {"id": 315707, "content": "冬天的东北，周末能呆的地方除了家就是商场了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528179}, {"id": 315709, "content": "老朋友见面，在商场餐厅吃个饭，转到楼下咖啡厅聊聊天，晚上KTV唱个歌，最后负一楼叫个车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527795}, {"id": 315710, "content": "谈恋爱搬进了商场", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364013}, {"id": 315715, "content": "想出门转悠，直接去商场", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525214}, {"id": 315725, "content": "吃饭，逛街，看电影，唱k，做美容，健身，买菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528245}, {"id": 319053, "content": "苹果手机每到冬天的时候，自动关机，我第一时间想的就是去商场让手机暖和点，看看能不能开机！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 315729, "content": "约会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 315742, "content": "赶论文在麦当劳？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067036}, {"id": 315747, "content": "朋友聊天从吃饭的地方到满记甜品、鲜芋仙等各种甜品店奶茶店...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508004}, {"id": 316012, "content": "除了玩游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307555}, {"id": 315773, "content": "生活被搬进了商场，商场被搬进了家里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528341}, {"id": 315774, "content": "所有商场都被同化了 尤其一线城市 里面服装饮食超市 有的时候有一瞬间忘记自己在别的城市旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1524869}, {"id": 315775, "content": "商场解决所有花钱需求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464799}, {"id": 315776, "content": "情侣约会去商场会增多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519927}, {"id": 315780, "content": "唱K", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831879}, {"id": 315781, "content": "谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528218}, {"id": 315783, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471969}, {"id": 315784, "content": "当然是拍照装B发朋友圈收赞", "image": "img/option/option/201812102220100An8ZQlhdYezDbEt.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248760}, {"id": 316297, "content": "逛吃逛吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1530751}, {"id": 315786, "content": "按摩不去推拿店，直接去商场电动按摩椅直接躺下", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528521}, {"id": 315787, "content": "吃、喝、拉、撒……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528537}, {"id": 315788, "content": "我怎么很难想出来，不太理解这句话。😭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 317087, "content": "不敢进商场，商场里都是生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534283}]}